### CRUD CATEGORIES

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:3007/api/v1/categories

### Get category by id
GET http://localhost:3007/api/v1/categories/1

### Post Create new category 
POST http://localhost:3111/api/v1/roles 
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Mascara Nica",
    "category_id": 7,
